{title: Prisoner's Prayer}
{artist: Hank Snow}
{composer: unknown}

Ted Daffan and Donald Nash
[G]In my cell so dark and [D7]dreary
The touch of God's hand I can [G]feel
Asking Him to please [C]forgive me
